surprises you, but I think

39:06.126 --> 39:08.824
that God forces us to move
on the earthly plane

39:08.868 --> 39:11.131
to bring in His kingdom.

39:11.174 --> 39:13.263
We want you to work
with David and us

39:13.307 --> 39:15.048
to stop Leland.

39:15.091 --> 39:18.443
