39:53.042 --> 39:55.436
I'm going to hug my daughter.

39:56.872 --> 39:58.700
Keep her in line.

39:59.701 --> 40:02.182
She's a mother.

40:02.225 --> 40:03.923
You need to stay in line.

40:03.966 --> 40:05.968
No, I'll be right there.

40:06.012 --> 40:09.276
Just do what they say.
We're coming right now.

40:09.319 --> 40:10.886
- Ben?
- No, Lilli.

40:10.930 --> 40:12.235
