41:22.305 --> 41:24.264
Renee?

41:28.747 --> 41:30.618
- Are-are you okay?

41:43.936 --> 41:46.547
- Yeshua.

41:46.591 --> 41:48.549
- Yeshua.

41:48.593 --> 41:50.812
- Are you all right?
- Uh... okay, all right.

41:53.119 --> 41:54.947
Yeshua.

41:54.990 --> 41:56.122
Yeshua.

41:56.165 --> 41:57.515
Are you all right?

41:57.558 --> 41:59.038
- Yeshua!

42:01.040 --> 42:04.173
- Okay, she said something...
- It's time for the sacrifice!

42:04.217 --> 42:06.393
Okay, uh, Renee,
I'll call you later, okay?

42:06.436 --> 42:09.483
Hey, hey, hey, hey!
Okay, okay. Excuse me.

42:09.527 --> 42:12.355
