45:19.847 --> 45:22.023
Owen, fight it! Fight it!

45:22.067 --> 45:23.329
Lilli!

45:23.372 --> 45:24.722
No!

45:24.765 --> 45:27.594
- No.
- No, no. It's okay. It's okay.

45:27.637 --> 45:29.030
- I'm here, Owen.
- I'm so sorry.

45:29.074 --> 45:30.815
I didn't know where you were.
I didn't.

45:30.858 --> 45:33.034
- Lilli, I'm so sorry.
- I'm here, Owen.

45:33.078 --> 45:35.994
- I love you.

45:43.392 --> 45:45.307
Hey, Ben, what's up?
How's it going?

45:49.224 --> 45:51.226
Ben?

45:51.270 --> 45:52.619
